; Coverage test for format.cc lines 272-284
; Test %$ field reference in secondary format (after %/).
; The %/ separator defines a secondary format for the 2nd+ postings in
; a transaction. %$N references the Nth expression field from the primary
; format template.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Expenses:Drink    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(account) %(amount)\n%/REF:%$1 %$2\n'
Expenses:Food $10.00
REF:Expenses:Drink $5.00
REF:Assets:Cash $-15.00
end test
